*********************BACKGROUND***********************
The sharpshooter came about in the year 2032, the world
called for a warrior with amazing gun control. You are
one of the elete members of soceity, Your profession is
known throughout the realms as one of the most fearsome
and powerful organizations. Go forth into these worlds
make a name for yourself and for the glory of Your Leader
Lord Irol Ecierif, the FireArms Master.
